# Plan 7: Homepage Hero & Featured Content

## Goal
Design a stunning homepage with a full-screen hero section and featured content.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create `app/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Design the Hero section with a large background image/video and artist branding.
- [ ] Add a "Listen Now" CTA that plays the latest release.
- [ ] Create a "Featured Music" section displaying the top tracks.
- [ ] Create a "Latest News" or "Upcoming Shows" teaser section.
- [ ] Implement parallax scrolling or scroll-triggered animations using Framer Motion.
